title: Governance and Leadership - IMU University
snippet: Each council member in the SRC is assigned to a particular section of the IMU experience. We have 16 council members in our Bukit Jalil Campus, and separate councils for our Clinical Campuses. The Senate is the highest academic body of the University and is responsible for University-wide policies.
